prod.full_name: Nike Vaporwaffle sacai Sesame Blue Void
prod.path: Home/Sneakers/Nike/Sacai/Nike Vaporwaffle Sacai Sesame Blue Void
prod.desciption:
The Nike Vaporwaffle sacai Sesame Blue Void is made of a Sesame textile upper with Sesame suede and leather overlays. Hits of Blue Void and white also appear on the Swoosh and heel wrap. Nike and sacai branding appears on the woven tongue labels and heel tabs. A black Waffle outsole completes the design.

The Nike Vaporwaffle sacai Sesame Blue Void released in April of 2021 and retailed for $180.
